---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = "Privacy Policy | C.A.Gs — Congo African Greys, Midland TX | Your Data Is Secure";
const description = "CongoAfricanGreys.com privacy policy. We protect your personal data with 7 clear rules. USDA-licensed, CITES-compliant African Grey parrot breeders. Midland, TX.";
const canonical = "https://congoafricangreys.com/privacy-policy/";
---

<BaseLayout {title} {description} {canonical}>

  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">

    <h1 class="font-lora text-3xl font-bold text-green mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: February 21, 2025</p>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">

      <p>At <a href="/">Congo African Greys (C.A.Gs)</a>, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information by providing a secure African Grey Parrot purchase experience for all our customers.</p>
      <p>This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you visit our website, purchase a parrot, or interact with us.</p>

      <!-- ToC -->
      <nav class="not-prose bg-cream border border-gold/30 rounded-xl p-5 mb-8" aria-label="Policy sections">
        <h2 class="font-lora font-semibold text-green text-base mb-3">Policy Sections</h2>
        <ol class="space-y-1 text-sm text-green/80 list-decimal list-inside">
          <li><a href="#information-we-collect" class="hover:text-clay transition-colors">Information We Collect</a></li>
          <li><a href="#how-we-use" class="hover:text-clay transition-colors">How We Use Your Information</a></li>
          <li><a href="#data-retention" class="hover:text-clay transition-colors">Data Retention &amp; Deletion</a></li>
          <li><a href="#data-protection" class="hover:text-clay transition-colors">How We Protect Your Data</a></li>
          <li><a href="#cookies" class="hover:text-clay transition-colors">Cookies &amp; Tracking Technologies</a></li>
          <li><a href="#third-party" class="hover:text-clay transition-colors">Third-Party Data Sharing</a></li>
          <li><a href="#your-rights" class="hover:text-clay transition-colors">Your Privacy Rights (GDPR &amp; CCPA)</a></li>
          <li><a href="#updates" class="hover:text-clay transition-colors">Updates to This Policy</a></li>
        </ol>
      </nav>

      <h2 id="information-we-collect">1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>We may collect the following personal information:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Personal Information</strong> — Name, email address, phone number, shipping/billing address.</li>
        <li><strong>Payment Information</strong> — Payment method details (Zelle or Cash App). We do not store credit card or bank details.</li>
        <li><strong>Order Information</strong> — Details about your purchased parrot, including species, age, and health records.</li>
        <li><strong>Communication Data</strong> — Any messages, emails, or customer support inquiries.</li>
        <li><strong>Website Usage Data</strong> — IP address, browser type, and pages visited on our site (collected via cookies).</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 id="how-we-use">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Order Fulfillment &amp; Delivery</strong> — To process payments, arrange shipping, and provide order updates.</li>
        <li><strong>Customer Support</strong> — To respond to inquiries and resolve issues.</li>
        <li><strong>Marketing &amp; Promotions</strong> — To send special offers, newsletters, and updates (only if you opt-in).</li>
        <li><strong>Fraud Prevention &amp; Security</strong> — To protect against unauthorized transactions.</li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>We never sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties unless required by law.</strong></p>

      <h2 id="data-retention">3. Data Retention &amp; Deletion</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>We retain personal data only as long as necessary to fulfill orders, provide customer support, and comply with legal obligations.</li>
        <li>You can request deletion of your personal information by <a href="/contact-us/">contacting us</a>.</li>
        <li>If legal obligations require us to retain certain information (such as tax or purchase records), we will notify you accordingly.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 id="data-protection">4. How We Protect Your Data</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Encrypted Transactions</strong> — Payment and sensitive data are securely encrypted.</li>
        <li><strong>Strict Access Controls</strong> — Only authorized personnel can access your data.</li>
        <li><strong>Regular Security Audits</strong> — We review and update security measures regularly.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 id="cookies">5. Cookies &amp; Tracking Technologies</h2>
      <p>We use cookies to enhance your browsing experience and analyze website traffic. Cookies help us:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Recognize repeat visitors and save preferences.</li>
        <li>Improve website functionality and performance.</li>
        <li>Track page visits and customer interactions.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>You can disable cookies in your browser settings if you prefer not to be tracked.</p>

      <h2 id="third-party">6. Third-Party Data Sharing</h2>
      <p>We only share necessary data with trusted third parties to complete transactions and improve services, including:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Shipping Carriers</strong> — To deliver parrots safely.</li>
        <li><strong>Payment Processors</strong> — To facilitate secure payments.</li>
        <li><strong>Veterinary Services</strong> — If health documentation is required.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>For more information on consumer data rights in the U.S., please visit:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://www.ftc.gov/business-guidance/privacy-security" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Federal Trade Commission (FTC) – Privacy &amp; Security</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.nist.gov/privacy-framework" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">National Institute of Standards and Technology (NIST) – Consumer Privacy Framework</a></li>
      </ul>

      <h2 id="your-rights">7. Your Privacy Rights (GDPR &amp; CCPA Compliance)</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Access &amp; Correction:</strong> You can request a copy of or corrections to your data.</li>
        <li><strong>Opt-Out:</strong> Unsubscribe from marketing emails anytime.</li>
        <li><strong>Data Deletion:</strong> Request permanent removal of your data unless required for legal purposes.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>📩 <a href="/contact-us/">Contact us for any privacy concerns</a>.</p>

      <h2 id="updates">8. Updates to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Please check back for the latest version. <strong>Last Updated: February 21, 2025.</strong></p>

    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="mt-12 bg-logo-dark text-cream rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-cream/80 mb-4">Have questions about your data? Our team is happy to help.</p>
      <a href="/contact-us/" class="inline-block bg-clay text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-full hover:bg-clay-dk transition-colors">Contact C.A.Gs →</a>
    </div>

  </section>

</BaseLayout>
